432
01:17:55.823 --> 01:17:58.281
Sommigen houden van kletsen.

433
01:18:06.656 --> 01:18:07.739
Virgilio.

434
01:18:11.489 --> 01:18:12.614
Cirù?

435
01:18:13.823 --> 01:18:16.448
Wij waren het niet.

436
01:18:16.573 --> 01:18:20.781
